   redis-cli -h CLUSTER.ENDPOINT.6379 --user DEFAULT --tls -a $(aws rds generate-db-auth-token --hostname CLUSTER.ENDPOINT.6379 --port 6379 --region us-east-1 --username DEFAULT)
   ```
4. **For IAM users**: Use access key credentials directly with `generate-db-auth-token`

